natambio (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging.
  * Split into natambio (real-time JACK client), natambio-tools (offline C
    FIR/DRC generators), natambio-ladspa (LADSPA plugin) and natambio-drc
    (offline Python toolkit).

